initab ignores the entire row when it calculates the correlation or covaria=
nce matrix. However, when you calculate the covariance matrix by itself, Mi=
nitab does not ignore entire rows in its calculations when there are missin=
g values. To obtain only the covariance matrix, choose <span class=3D"ph"><=
